[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0056","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0056.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1607","title":"Joomla! WMI (com_wmi) 组件 目录遍历本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Webmoney Web Merchant Interface（WMI，组件名 com_wmi）1.5.0 版本 wmi.php 中存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。攻击者通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数注入包含 ../ 的路径遍历序列，可包含并执行目标服务器上的任意本地文件，进而实现远程代码执行。该漏洞无需身份认证即可被远程利用，攻击条件仅需网络可达且目标启用了存在缺陷的 WMI 组件，CVSS 2.0 基础评分 6.8（中危）。成功利用后可读取敏感配置、执行恶意代码，严重威胁服务器安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1607"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2010-04-29","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用以存在缺陷的 com_wmi（Webmoney Web Merchant Interface）组件，或在 wmi.php/index.php 中对 controller 参数进行严格的白名单校验，过滤 ../ 等路径遍历字符；通过 .htaccess 限制对该组件脚本的访问，并关注 Joomla! 官方安全更新以升级至修复版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/63979","http://secunia.com/advisories/39539","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12316","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39608","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58032"],"poc_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12316"],"exp_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12316"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0056.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0054","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0054.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1602","title":"Joomla! ZiMB Comment 0.8.1 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 ZiMB Comment（com_zimbcomment）组件 0.8.1 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。该漏洞源于程序对 index.php 的 controller 参数未进行充分过滤，攻击者可通过在该参数中注入 '../' 序列进行路径穿越，从而读取服务器上的任意文件，可能导致敏感信息泄露。此漏洞 CVSS 评分为 7.5 危害等级为高，攻击者无需身份验证即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1602"],"sources":["cve","nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-29","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Joomla! ZiMB Comment 组件至 0.8.2 或更高版本以修复目录遍历漏洞。如需立即缓解，可在后台禁用 com_zimbcomment 组件，或在 WAF 层面拦截包含 '../' 的 controller 参数请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlazimbcomment-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12283","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39548","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0932","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12283","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1602.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1602.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1602.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1602.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1602-1742.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1602-1741.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-1602_9.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/cve-2010-1602-1740.yaml","https://github.com/TheMirkin/CVE-List-Public-Exploits/blob/f496d51148a2b151f14fe6d0bef5b42ee27f6ccb/CVE%20List/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1602.json","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12283"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0054.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0053","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0053.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1601","title":"Joomla! JA Comment 组件 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JA Comment（com_jacomment）组件存在目录遍历漏洞，其 index.php 在处理 view 参数时未对用户输入做充分校验与过滤。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需在请求 index.php 的 view 参数中构造包含 ..（点-点）的恶意路径序列，即可越权读取目标服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源码、密码等敏感信息）。该漏洞影响所有安装了存在缺陷版本 JA Comment 组件的 Joomla! 站点，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标 Web 服务并发送特制 HTTP 请求即可，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级为中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1601"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-29","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"建议立即升级 JA Comment 组件到官方发布的最新修复版本；若暂无法升级，可在后台扩展管理中停用或卸载 com_jacomment 组件以彻底消除风险。同时应在组件控制器中对 view 参数进行白名单校验，过滤 ../ 与空字节等非法字符，并在 Web 服务器层（如 Apache 的 .htaccess）限制对敏感路径参数的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlajacomment-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39472","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12236","http://www.osvdb.org/63802","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39516","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57848","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12236","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1601.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1601.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1601.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1601.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1601-1737.yaml","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1601.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder5/cve-2010-1601-1736.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/foreztgump/cve_json/blob/b5f345eafeb97dce3fe03de3869b187e0574a5c0/2010/CVE-2010-1601.json","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/cve-2010-1601-1735.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1601_2.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0053.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0031","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0031.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1429","title":"红帽 JBoss Enterprise Application Platform 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Red Hat JBoss Enterprise Application Platform（JBoss EAP）4.2.0.CP09 之前版本及 4.3.0.CP08 之前版本中存在访问控制漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 status servlet 发送带有 full=true 参数的恶意请求，绕过权限检查获取已部署 Web 应用的敏感上下文信息。该漏洞源于 CVE-2008-3273 修复不完整导致的回归问题，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。受影响的版本包括 JBoss EAP 4.2.0 系列及 4.3.0 系列，建议升级至 CP09/CP08 及以上版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1429"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-28T22:30:00.840","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:22.633","remediation":"升级 JBoss EAP 至 4.2.0.CP09 或 4.3.0.CP08 及以上版本（对应 RHSA-2010:0376/RHSA-2010:0377）。如无法立即升级，可在反向代理或防火墙层面限制对 /status 及 /JMX 端点的外部访问，仅允许可信任管理 IP 访问；同时禁用 status servlet 的 full=true 参数查询功能，或直接移除部署中的 status-invoker.sar 组件作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=132698550418872&w=2","http://secunia.com/advisories/39563","http://securitytracker.com/id?1023918","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39710","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0992","https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=585900","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58149","https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2010-0376.html","https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2010-0377.html","https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2010-0378.html","https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2010-0379.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/44009/","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1429.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1429.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1429.yaml","https://github.com/CCrashBandicot/helpful/blob/336b2c95b482d6c9de7756109b2699c7cfd8545c/CVE-2010-1429.txt","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-1429.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/35622681f0b1b2e88f53f70590ed8e8540eebf1f/references/CVE-2010-1429-2023-09-21-1730_1","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/faaab442a02d3e0621b98b9cb588f9f3801b024d/2010/CVE-2010-1429.json","https://github.com/bugbountywithmarco/bugbounty-disclosed-reports/blob/b6c76d1437e08a0ef77b7fbed612791c71cc4aa5/reports/2375659_CVE-2010-1429_JBoss_Insecure_Storage_of_Sensitive_Information_on_ipsmtncoug.md","https://github.com/method-security/webscan/blob/ddfe93858ef377a10027023c31d31aa08d46bfda/utils/nuclei/templates/pentest/scan/cve/2010/CVE-2010-1429.yaml","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/vulncheck-oss/0day.today.archive/blob/3664abdd71985a44aff3260896a8f36e2f4a9682/remote-exploits/29751.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0031.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0052","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0052.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1586","title":"惠普系统管理主页 - 'RedirectUrl' 参数 URL 重定向漏洞","description":"惠普系统管理主页（System Management Homepage）是一款为服务器管理的IT管理员提供的综合工具，可预测、诊断和快速响应潜在或实际的系统故障。攻击者可通过SMH的可信URL漏洞利用RedirectUrl参数劫持受害者跳转到任意恶意网站，进而利用浏览器漏洞进一步攻击受害者操作系统并实现远程代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1586"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb","hp","nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到惠普系统管理主页v6.2或更高版本以修复漏洞，建议安装供应商发布的最新补丁和安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T11:00:54.047473758+00:00","references":["http://yehg.net/lab/pr0js/advisories/hp_system_management_homepage_url_redirection_abuse","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39676","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58107","http://h20000.www2.hp.com/bizsupport/TechSupport/Document.jsp?objectID=c02518794&lang=en&cc=us&taskId=101&prodSeriesId=344313&prodTypeId=18964","http://yehg.net/lab/pr0js/advisories/hp_system_management_homepage_url_redirection_abuse"],"poc_urls":["http://x.x.x.x:2301/red2301.html?RedirectUrl=evil@attacker.com"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0052.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0050","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1535","title":"Joomla! TRAVELbook 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 TRAVELbook（com_travelbook）组件 1.0.1 版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞，其根源在于组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分的路径过滤与校验。远程、无需身份认证的攻击者可通过向 index.php 提交包含“../”（点点）序列的恶意 controller 参数，突破目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源代码、敏感凭证等）。该漏洞影响安装并启用了 TRAVELbook 1.0.1 组件的 Joomla! 网站，攻击仅需构造特制 URL 发起 HTTP 请求即可，可造成敏感信息泄露，并可能被进一步利用产生其他未明影响。建议用户及时升级或停用存在漏洞的组件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1535"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26T18:30:00.753","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:34.427","remediation":"建议立即升级 Joomla! TRAVELbook 组件至 1.0.2 或更高版本，官方已修复该目录遍历漏洞。若暂时无法升级，可在 Joomla 后台禁用 com_travelbook 组件，或在 Web 应用防火墙配置规则拦截包含 \"../\" 等目录遍历序列的 controller 参数请求。同时建议将 PHP 配置中 open_basedir 限制在网站根目录，限制 PHP 文件读取范围作为纵深防御。建议定期检查 Joomla 官方安全公告及时更新所有扩展组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39254","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12151","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12151","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1535.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1535.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1535.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bef45ac8bcc9ee2ca44f6ae8c25801f320761c2b/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1535.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-1535-1725.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-1535-1724.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder3/CVE-2010-1535.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1535-1728.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1535_7.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1535.js","https://github.com/0isagoodnumber/nuclei_templates/blob/7399a62723d05863ea3f5c2d96b8fe71a1f0ced0/templates/CVE-2010-1535.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0050.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2010/EXP-AVE-2010-0050.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0048","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0048.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1534","title":"Joomla Shoutbox Pro 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Shoutbox Pro（com_shoutbox）组件 1.3 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传递包含 `..`（点点）的恶意路径，绕过访问控制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于组件未对用户输入的路径参数进行充分的过滤与验证，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，结合公开的 PoC 可实现敏感信息泄露。影响范围包括使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1534"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26T18:30:00.723","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:34.317","remediation":"建议立即卸载 Joomla! Shoutbox Pro 组件，或升级到已修复路径遍历漏洞的最新版本。如无官方补丁，可直接删除或禁用 com_shoutbox 组件目录，并在 .htaccess 中添加规则过滤 `controller` 参数中的 `..` 路径遍历字符作为临时缓解。对于不再维护的第三方扩展，迁移到替代组件是最彻底的修复方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/63562","http://secunia.com/advisories/39352","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12067","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39213","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57534","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12067","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1534.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1534.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1534.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1534.js","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-1534.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-1534-1720.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1534_40.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1534_4.yaml","https://github.com/Kaiz7703/My_Tools/blob/a1512a65d2b2896963bf459cd1edcdab0a9bdcba/nuclei-waf-testing/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1534.yaml","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1534.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-1534-1719.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0048.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0047","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1533","title":"Joomla! TweetLA 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 TweetLA（com_tweetla）组件 1.0.1 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 index.php 文件的 controller 参数传入包含 ..（点点）的恶意路径，实现任意文件读取，导致网站敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响运行 Joomla! CMS 并启用该组件的网站系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1533"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26T18:30:00.690","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:34.207","remediation":"立即卸载 Joomla! 后台已安装的 TweetLA 组件（com_tweetla），或在服务器上删除 components/com_tweetla/ 目录。如仍需类似功能，选择仍在维护的替代组件。同时配置 Web 应用防火墙（如 ModSecurity）拦截路径遍历特征，规则示例：`SecRule ARGS:controller \"@contains ..\" \"id:1001,deny\"`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39258","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12142","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12142","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1533.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1533.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1533.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bef45ac8bcc9ee2ca44f6ae8c25801f320761c2b/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1533.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-1533-1715_1.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-1533.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1533_3.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Dec/11/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-1533.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder2/cve-2010-1533-1717.yaml","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1533.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0046","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1532","title":"Joomla! PowerMail Pro 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 PowerMail Pro 组件 1.5.3 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数中传入包含 `..`（点点）的恶意路径，实现任意文件读取。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的路径参数进行充分过滤，可读取系统敏感文件如配置文件等，可能导致进一步的信息泄露。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1532"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26T18:30:00.660","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:34.100","remediation":"立即在 Joomla 后台卸载 com_powermail 组件（PowerMail Pro 1.5.3），该扩展已停止维护不再有安全更新。替换为仍在维护的其他 Joomla 邮件表单扩展。若暂时无法卸载，可在 Apache/Nginx 或 WAF 层面添加规则，拦截 controller 参数中包含 `../` 或 `..%2f` 等目录遍历特征的 GET 请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlapowermail-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39226","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12118","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39348","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12118","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1532.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1532.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/htt